Subject: RE: Application for Amended SW 
Date: Thu, 22 Oct 2020 17:22:54 +0000 
On this same subject, since I spoke with you this morning, I have also had a call with about this, so our agents are 
now aware of the issue. I think you also asked about the status of the image review: said it's underway and they 
understand it needs to be completed by the deadline. 
Thanks very much for your guidance on this —  if you have any other questions before you speak with.or if any 
additional information would be useful, please let us know. 
Thanks, 
From 
Sent: Thursday, October 22, 2020 1:07 PM 
To 
Cc• 
Subject: Application for Amended SW 
Chiefs, 
Thanks very much for talking this morning. As discussed, attached is a draft application for an amended search warrant 
correcting the FBI barcode numbers for 3 devices that were seized from Epstein's NY residence. In case it's useful, I'm also 
attaching the exhibits that are referenced in the draft application. 
Thanks, 
EFTA00017800
